    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172770/extras/1df171a36f230b1606a351c93e0a7a40.avif?t=1763490276\" width=630 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172770/extras/6bc986775ddff8fddddb336af0001c33.poster.avif?t=1763490276\" width=630 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172770/extras/6bc986775ddff8fddddb336af0001c33.webm?t=1763490276\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172770/extras/6bc986775ddff8fddddb336af0001c33.mp4?t=1763490276\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你和最多三位线上合作伙伴被吸入一台被疯狂、毁灭性病毒占据的街机。收集能量球为安全室充能，并抵御它的无休止攻击。你能坚持到揭开谜团并逃脱吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172770/extras/39421233bbe150042bf94fef8a9aa4bf.avif?t=1763490276\" width=630 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172770/extras/682d2c61621b34a05b881c88cb7f115d.poster.avif?t=1763490276\" width=630 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172770/extras/682d2c61621b34a05b881c88cb7f115d.webm?t=1763490276\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172770/extras/682d2c61621b34a05b881c88cb7f115d.mp4?t=1763490276\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >能量球就是能量。妥善管理资源，你就能购买升级和特殊物品，应对途中各种奇异挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172770/extras/d871fceeb713eef5ccfd4edc938da688.avif?t=1763490276\" width=630 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你会选择哪些物品？从朴素的手电筒，到爽快的高压清洗器，再到可以在地图房间中生成指示箭头的升级——这座迷宫中充满了奇异而实用的东西。但它们究竟来自何处？你能揭开迷宫的隐藏秘密吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172770/extras/9be972a2083da2c698bdee84361065e3.avif?t=1763490276\" width=630 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172770/extras/23457a63153626a4ddc3d46faebe6ab5.poster.avif?t=1763490276\" width=630 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172770/extras/23457a63153626a4ddc3d46faebe6ab5.webm?t=1763490276\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172770/extras/23457a63153626a4ddc3d46faebe6ab5.mp4?t=1763490276\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个充满异常实体的高响应世界，带来无尽的惊吓与笑声。成功避开“易容者”、隐形跟踪者、口袋维度怪物，而就在你以为安全时，转角突然与“Ms Croak-Man”面对面——或者说，与她变成的某种存在相遇。[ /p]</p>",
